·

ONCOLOGY

—

INCLUDES REVENUES FROM HUMAN PRESCRIPTION PHARMACEUTICAL PRODUCTS ADDRESSING ONCOLOGY AND ONCOLOGY-RELATED ILLNESSES. THE PRODUCTS IN THIS BUSINESS UNIT IN 2012 INCLUDE

INLYTA

,

SUTENT

