OUR BUSINESSES ARE HEAVILY REGULATED IN MOST OF THE COUNTRIES IN WHICH WE OPERATE. IN THE U.S., THE PRINCIPAL AUTHORITY REGULATING OUR OPERATIONS IS THE U.S. FOOD AND DRUG ADMINISTRATION (FDA). THE FDA REGULATES THE SAFETY AND EFFICACY OF THE PRODUCTS WE OFFER AND OUR RESEARCH, QUALITY, MANUFACTURING PROCESSES, PRODUCT PROMOTION, ADVERTISING AND PRODUCT LABELING. SIMILAR REGULATIONS EXIST IN MOST OTHER COUNTRIES, AND IN MANY COUNTRIES THE GOVERNMENT ALSO REGULATES OUR PRICES. SEE

GOVERNMENT REGULATION AND PRICE CONSTRAINTS

BELOW.

